00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:36.360
 his members. But Waldo posing as a little genius, develops a mechanical device, 

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:40.910
 connected to him by a glove and a harness, which allows him to reproduce the desired movements. 

00:00:40.910 --> 00:00:45.820
 Moreover the scientific apparatus allowing to carry out manipulations under cover 

00:00:45.820 --> 00:00:49.840
 mechanical arms are now called waldoes in reference to this news. 

