 In the form of light armor, the prototypes presented allow to increase 

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:39.240
 physical strength, offer anti-projectile protection and monitor, thanks to 

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:43.340
 sensors, the vital data of the wearer. Still in test phase at the moment, 

00:01:43.340 --> 00:01:48.250
 the first armor should be operational in 2018. Even if we are far from 

00:01:48.250 --> 00:01:51.900
 the powerful armor of Iron Man, let's admit it's a great bet 

